  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エターナルソードは王都で管理する。
心配するな。　
悪用はしないし、誰にも触れさせない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Eternal Sword will be dealt with in the
royal capital. Don't worry. It won't be misused,
and nobody will be allowed to come into
contact with it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うん、それだったら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah, in that case...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>待て！　なにか妙な気配が！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wait! I'm sensing something odd!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>聖剣の守護者は敗れたか。
手間が省けたな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So the holy sword's guardian has been defeated.
That saves times.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>誰だ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Who're you?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エターナルソードは返してもらう
この世界をやり直す為に……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Return the Eternal Sword to me.
I must remake this world...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ぐぁ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Gah!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオン！　大丈夫か！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon! Are you alright?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>強い！　まさかこいつが
エルレインが言ってた男なのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He's strong!
Could this be the man Elraine talked about?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>人間に救う価値などなかった。
彼らの犠牲は……無駄だったのだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Humans were not worth saving.
Their sacrifices... amounted to nothing.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Duke is not speaking of the present here. He is speaking in past tense.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>35</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>どういう意味！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What do you mean by that?!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>消えた！
エターナルソードを……奪われた……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>He disappeared!
The Eternal Sword... He's stolen it...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>26</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
